{"tid":720333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[講插水？] 拉舒福特指盧卡古鬥心似C朗","createTime":"2018-06-28T00:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T01:40:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e47f1053cdbb2db48ba503e43e0c81506468efd0","tid":720333,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"拉舒福特指盧卡古鬥心似C朗<br />\n澳洲輸越位波 VAR冇料到<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古在世界盃分組賽2場入4球，與C朗的入球數字相同。但是他可能因為受傷未能踢下場比賽，需要休戰一場。<br />\n<br />\n拉舒福特大讚盧卡古與C朗拿度十分相似：「他們都是有鬥心，一直想自己進步。正如在曼聯我們經常收操之後練習埋門，這才是應有的態度。」"},{"pid":"9f55c4186dd601080356df51371e0aa1c64ffcc5","tid":720333,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"美欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002ad0fdc5784b9d4c7c93d507e2b8418153fd1e","tid":720333,"uid":190749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:24:59.000Z","msg":"harry claim 宜家5球<br />\n咁佢更好鬥心?"},{"pid":"dda61d802d337a84e4f056971621fe2fb1f35e85","tid":720333,"uid":4431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002ad0fdc5784b9d4c7c93d507e2b8418153fd1e","tid":720333,"uid":190749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:24:59.000Z","msg":"harry claim 宜家5球<br />\n咁佢更好鬥心?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"用12碼嚟攞金球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}